{"tid":1024481,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)猿人爭霸戰 千騙萬化 侏羅紀世界","createTime":"2019-02-16T14:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T19:40:45.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfb2cbd0cea99fcd398fb11907463c57ae80293","tid":1024481,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=6a053a67\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=fc3a77fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=91016c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7d/Planet_of_the_Apes_%282001%29_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7d%2FPlanet_of_the_Apes_%25282001%2529_poster.jpg&h=18f668ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fd/Focus_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffd%2FFocus_Poster.jpg&h=3e403d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e7/Jurassic_Park_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe7%2FJurassic_Park_poster.jpg&h=7dee0461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.公元2029年，人類為了尋求更大的生活空間而前往其他星球發展。在尋找適合的星球的途中，人類開始用某種新技術培養猩猩，使牠們的學習能力變強，讓猩猩代替人類完成一些簡單的工作。在一次星際巡察任務中，身為太空人男主角的猩猩，所駕駛的飛船遭遇了宇宙黑洞與太空基地失去聯繫。為了拯救自己的搭檔，男主角不顧阻攔獨自一人駕駛飛船到星際進行搜索。可是，最終飛船墜毀到了一個陌生的星球上<br />\n<br />\n2.主要故事由詐騙老練技巧的尼基&middot;吉翁（威爾&middot;史密斯飾）走去夜總會一趟，遇上新手騙子傑斯&middot;芭蕾特（瑪格&middot;羅比飾）為徒，之後進行向謝力源（黃榮亮飾）作為對賭。3年後，尼基&middot;吉翁成為格雷格（羅德里格&middot;桑托羅飾）賽車東主為下屬，期間再遇到傑斯&middot;芭蕾特為保持對方關係，後來被賽車東主識破後，尼基與傑斯被五花大綁來進行依法炮製<br />\n<br />\n3.侏羅紀公園發生慘劇後22年，最初的公園創辦人約翰&middot;哈蒙德經營的『遺傳科技公司（InGen）』在瀕臨破產下被『馬斯拉尼國際企業（Masrani Corp）』收購。在企業老闆賽門&middot;馬斯拉尼的經營下，昔日公園的所在地「努布拉島」已經被企業重新建造，如今成為了一個安全指數百分之百且嶄新的恐龍主題樂園，並更名為「侏羅紀世界」。久而久之，當公園的遊客們已經開始對恐龍感到厭倦時，企業為了再度提升來遊客人數而決定創造新賣點，在生命開發實驗室的亨利&middot;吳博士在賽門的要求下創造出了一隻基因混合恐龍，命名為「帝王暴龍」.........<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=8fd4776b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=39ed0dd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec853f7432abc47fe7dbb91e0c173aaaf852e99","tid":1